decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: 2-2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Than.QN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Trong l\u00fac H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110VK\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 th\u00ec chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Than.QN l\u1ea1i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 thua v\u00e0 h\u00f2a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL t\u1ea1i Pleiku \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16, Than.QN \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt ra kh\u1ecfi Top 3. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c tinh th\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00e0 trong t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra r\u1eb1ng, li\u1ec7u Than.QN c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1edfi 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Than.QN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u201ckh\u1eafc tinh\u201d c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd trong nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 4-4 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 26 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u1ec3 r\u01a1i ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0o tay Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n kh\u00f3 \u201cnu\u1ed1t\u201d tr\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Than.QN.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e1 v\u1edbi Than.QN ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf V.League, Than.QN l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1 k\u1ef5 gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1\u201d, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\nadblox.net<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Than.QN c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1i t\u00f4i, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3! <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3905","checkdouble":"190056"},{"date":"08:21 01/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-quang-nam-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-17-thu-thach-san-khach.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch?</h2><h2>Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 1/2 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tr\u1eadn thua m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 &lsquo;y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng v\u00eda&rsquo; tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Qu\u1ea3ng gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17) Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 17) Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Quang-Nam-vs-HAGL-(17h00-ngay-17)-Thu-thach-san-khach-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u01afu th\u1ebf \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u00e0 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.&nbsp;Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Claudecir v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac b\u1edfi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1ecd li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn trong l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eabn \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a ch\u00edn mu\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u00f2n non nh\u01b0 HAGL, th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn sai l\u1ea7m khi m\u1ea3i m\u00ea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. V\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 thua c\u00f3 1/23 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Do v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac gi\u1eef 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HAGL v\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, CLB HAGL c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y do anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a HAGL khi anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo;. V\u00ec th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u1eabn Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf 2 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. S\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi h\u1ecd ghi t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp. V\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, HAGL t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 2 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng &lsquo;ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n&rsquo; trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 c\u1ee7a G\u1ed7. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Qu\u1ea3ng Nam s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi, bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 16\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 16\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 17</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL th\u1eafng 1, thua 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 t\u1edbi nay, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau 11 l\u1ea7n, trong \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam th\u1eafng 5, HAGL th\u1eafng 4, hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau 2 l\u1ea7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Claudecir v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng; V\u0103n H\u1ecdc, Papel, V\u0103n H\u00e0, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Thanh Trung, H\u1eefu Ph\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1eafng, Huy H\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Th\u1ea1nh, Quang Huy.<br>\r\nHAGL: V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn; V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Anh T\u00e0i, H\u1ed3ng Duy, A S\u00e2n, A Ho\u00e0ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Osmar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: 2-2.</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu-168-189946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu-168-189946.html\">HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a V-League 2018 mang t\u00ean Josip Zeba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Croatia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat-168-189842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat-168-189842.html\">HAGL m\u1ea5t C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League v\u00ec \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a V-League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-16-vleague-hagl-goi-ha-noi-tra-loi-168-189833.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/sau-vong-16-vleague-hagl-goi-ha-noi-tra-loi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-16-vleague-hagl-goi-ha-noi-tra-loi-168-189833.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League: HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3904","checkdouble":"190060"},{"date":"14:12 30/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tien-dao-mbappe-dung-tien-thuong-tai-world-cup-2018-de-lam-tu-thien.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3903","checkdouble":"189990"},{"date":"19:39 30/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 30/6: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i \u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/22/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-306-mu-va-chelsea-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 30/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 30/6.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>MU v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i &ldquo;Bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 306 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i Bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 306 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i Bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-306-MU-va-Chelsea-sap-trao-doi-Bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Willian v\u00e0 Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u1eefa Anthony Martial v\u00e0 Willian. HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0m &ldquo;v\u1eadt t\u1ebf th\u1ea7n&rdquo;. Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Martial.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo AS, Napoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema, HLV Carlo Ancelotti mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo. Napoli c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thibaut Courtois cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pjanic khang dinh chi trich Juventus la khong cong bang\" title=\"Pjanic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Man-City-muon-mua-Miralem-Pjanic-nhung-khong-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n 85 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Pjanic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 85 tri\u1ec7u euro, hi\u1ec7n Liverpool v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton s\u1eafp c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Kieran Tierney c\u1ee7a Celtic, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Tierney.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Uruguay: &quot;Ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Uruguay &ndash; HLV Tabarez chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng coi tr\u1ecdng Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-uruguay-chang-ai-co-the-ngan-chan-ronaldo-421-189996.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/hlv-uruguay-chang-ai-co-the-ngan-chan-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-uruguay-chang-ai-co-the-ngan-chan-ronaldo-421-189996.html\">HLV Uruguay: Ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Uruguay &ndash; HLV Tabarez chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng coi tr\u1ecdng Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Evening Standard, Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Leon Bailey v\u00e0 Anthony Martial, h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 120 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: &quot;N\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm v\u00e0o Ronaldo, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua ch\u1eafc&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Santos c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, song kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Seleccao kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o CR7.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac-421-189994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac-421-189994.html\">HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: N\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm v\u00e0o Ronaldo, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua ch\u1eafc</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Arsenal s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Calum Chambers</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sports News, Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Calum Chambers. HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u01b0a th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Fosu-Mensah&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fosu-Mensah\" title=\"Fosu-Mensah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/7/sao-tre-tiet-lo-ly-do-bo-ajax-vi-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Valencia h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Fosu-Mensah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Valencia mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Timothy Fosu-Mensah c\u1ee7a M.U. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 ch\u01a1i cho Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3902","checkdouble":"190003"},{"date":"20:36 30/06","title":"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-muon-chi-50-trieu-bang-cho-cau-thu-nguoi-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia th\u00edch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Pedro, b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic thay Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic thay Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Chelsea-muon-mua-Christian-Pulisic-thay-Willian-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Willian \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Conte \u1edf l\u1ea1i Willian s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u1ec9 khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y m\u1edbi t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-willian-cho-barca-nhung-mu-thi-khac-172-189983.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U v\u1eabn \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao Willian</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Pulisic thay Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Pulisic\" title=\"Christian Pulisic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/chelsea-muon-chi-50-trieu-bang-cho-cau-thu-nguoi-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Christian Pulisic thay Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChristian Pulisic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Dortmund trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Brige, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn, The Blues c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec M.U v\u00e0 Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Christian Pulisic, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3901","checkdouble":"190005"},{"date":"20:48 30/06","title":"MU mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/29/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Kop, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Lyon y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nabil Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-co-nguy-co-that-bai-vu-fekir-172-187705.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon</span>. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f2n c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverrpool, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverrpool, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, theo \u0111\u00f3 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Nabil Fekir anh s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Liverpool c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Coutinho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean-Michel Aulas c\u1ee7a Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o\u00a0s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o t\u1eeb The Kop n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Nabil Fekir</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Kop, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Lyon y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nabil Fekir\" title=\"Nabil Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm Fekir nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Trong 29 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Martial \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3900","checkdouble":"190006"},{"date":"13:20 30/06","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 ch\u1edd v\u1ee3 sinh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/30/tuyen-thu-anh-roi-world-cup-2018-ve-nha-cho-vo-sinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fabian Delph \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u1eb7c c\u00e1ch cho t\u1ea1m r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh t\u1ea1i Nga  \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 b\u00ean c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Natalie s\u1eafp sinh con.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Delph v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn Anh thua B\u1ec9 0-1 h\u00f4m 28/6. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u00ec t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H, kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabian Delph r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 ch\u1edd v\u1ee3 sinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabian Delph r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 ch\u1edd v\u1ee3 sinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/delph-6142-1530292241.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Delph (s\u1ed1 17) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate c\u1ea5p chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 ri\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh. \u1ea2nh: MadeInFoot.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Delph \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p t\u1ea1m r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3n ng\u01b0\u1eddi con th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f9ng c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Natalie. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 3 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 bay t\u1eeb Nga tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh. Delph, sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Colombia, di\u1ec5n ra sau \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Gareth Southgate l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\", Delph chia s\u1ebb. \"\u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p t\u00f4i t\u1ea1m r\u1eddi tuy\u1ec3n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 Phil Jones n\u1eefa. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, gia \u0111\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate c\u0169ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a John Stones. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng thay Stones sau hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i do th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Stones kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, John Stones ph\u1ea3i ch\u01b0\u1eddm \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n khi ng\u1ed3i xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u201cTam s\u01b0\u201d t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng\u201d, v\u00e0 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng 30/6 theo gi\u1edd Nga, t\u1ea1i Zelenogorsk.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3898","checkdouble":"189991"}]}